Kenshi Online Multiplayer System
Version: 2.0.0
Build Date: 2025-01-14
Codename: "Complete Remake - Production Ready"

Components:
- KenshiOnline.Launcher: v2.0.0 (NEW! Unified application)
- KenshiOnline.Core: v2.0.0
- KenshiOnline.Server: v2.0.0 (Legacy, use Launcher)
- KenshiOnline.ClientService: v2.0.0 (Legacy, use Launcher)
- Re_Kenshi_Plugin: v2.0.0

Game Modes:
- Solo Mode: One-click local multiplayer (NEW!)
- Host Mode: Server with auto IP detection (NEW!)
- Join Mode: Client with connection strings (NEW!)

Multiplayer Features:
- Full entity synchronization (Players, NPCs, Items)
- Server-authoritative combat and inventory
- Dynamic world state (time, weather, game speed)
- Chat system (5 channels: Global, Squad, Proximity, Whisper, System)
- Squad/Party system (up to 8 members)
- Friend system (up to 100 friends)
- Trading system (secure player-to-player)
- Admin commands (20+ commands)
- Session management with heartbeat
- Spatial optimization (100m grid)
- 20 Hz server updates with delta sync

Quality of Life:
- PLAY.bat: One-click launcher (NEW!)
- Build_Plugin.bat: Automated C++ build (NEW!)
- Server history: Last 10 servers saved (NEW!)
- Connection strings: Easy server sharing (NEW!)
- Auto-configuration: IP detection, ports (NEW!)
- Settings persistence: JSON config (NEW!)

Languages:
- English (Full support)
- Russian / Русский (Полная поддержка)

Build Information:
- Target Framework: .NET 8.0
- C++ Standard: C++17
- Platform: Windows 10/11 (64-bit)
- Game Version: Kenshi 1.0.68 (GOG recommended)

